lse\">!</mo><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P XOR Q = (P \\&amp; !Q) \\lVert (!P \\&amp; Q)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">PXORQ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">∥(</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Produire des tables de vérité pour :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P \\&amp; !Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">!P \\&amp;  !Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">∥</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">!P \\lVert !Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mopen\">∥</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P \\&amp; Q \\&amp; R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>Q</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">!P \\&amp;  !Q \\&amp;  !R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mclose\">!</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>R</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">∥</mo><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mi>Q</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&amp;</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P \\&amp; Q \\&amp; R \\lVert P \\&amp;  !Q \\&amp; R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\">&amp;</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><